  "_comment_gs1us_mapping": [
    "Receiving CTE per GS1 US 'EPCIS Recommendations for FSMA 204 CTEs' R2.0, §7.",
    "Pattern used: 'Aggregation Observe' variant (§7, pages 42-44).",
    "A prior TransformationEvent (creating_class_instance) is included for completeness — it documents",
    "the origin of the TLCs being received. In practice the upstream party captures this event; the receiver",
    "references it via sourceList.",
    "",
    "Receiving event itself:",
    "  AggregationEvent, action=OBSERVE, bizStep=receiving, disposition=in_progress.",
    "  parentID = SSCC Digital Link of the shipped pallet.",
    "  childQuantityList.epcClass = TLC (GTIN+Batch/Lot) KDE + product description + quantity/uom KDEs.",
    "  readPoint = Location GLN where the food was received KDE.",
    "  sourceList type=location = immediate previous source location GLN KDE.",
    "  destinationList type=location = receiving location GLN.",
    "  bizTransactionList type=recadv = reference document type + number KDEs.",
    "NO fsma: extension fields ride inside the event."
  ],
